tosdr.case: Users agree not to submit libelous, harassing or threatening content

title: Users agree not to submit libelous, harassing or threatening content
quoteText: Without limitation, we may do so to address UGC that comes to our attention that we believe is offensive, obscene, violent, harassing, threatening, abusive, illegal or otherwise objectionable or inappropriate, or to enforce the rights of third parties or these terms of use or any applicable additional terms.
